## 3. System Architecture

### 3.1 High-Level Architecture

Finance Buddy follows a **three-tier architecture**: a React frontend SPA, a Node.js/Express REST API backend, and a PostgreSQL database. All AI inference is delegated to the Anthropic Claude API. Market data is sourced from a third-party financial data provider.

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                        CLIENT TIER                              │
│  React 18 SPA (Vite + TypeScript + Tailwind + Zustand)          │
│  ┌──────────┬──────────┬──────────┬──────────┬────────────┐     │
│  │Dashboard │ Budget   │Portfolio │  Chat    │   Learn    │     │
│  │          │ Tracker  │& Watch   │  (SSE)   │            │     │
│  └──────────┴──────────┴──────────┴──────────┴────────────┘     │
└───────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────┘
                            │ HTTPS / JWT Bearer
┌───────────────────────────▼─────────────────────────────────────┐
│                        API TIER                                 │
│  Node.js 20 + Express 5 REST API                                │
│  ┌──────────┬──────────┬──────────┬──────────┬────────────┐     │
│  │Auth      │Budget    │Portfolio │Chat      │ AI Prompt  │     │
│  │Middleware│Endpoints │Endpoints │Streaming │ Builder    │     │
│  └──────────┴──────────┴──────────┴──────────┴────────────┘     │
│                    │              │              │               │
│          ┌────────▼──┐   ┌──────▼──────┐  ┌───▼──────────┐    │
│          │ Prisma ORM│   │ Polygon.io  │  │ Claude API   │    │
│          └────────┬──┘   │ Market Data │  │ (Anthropic)  │    │
│                   │      └─────────────┘  └──────────────┘    │
└───────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                    │
┌───────────────────▼─────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                        DATA TIER                                │
│  PostgreSQL 15                                                  │
│  Users · Profiles · Budgets · Holdings · InsightCards · Chat    │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Key Principle:** The backend acts as a trusted proxy for all Claude API calls. The frontend **never** holds or transmits an Anthropic API key.

### 3.2 Component Overview

| Component | Description | AI Role |
|-----------|-------------|---------|
| **React Frontend (SPA)** | All UI screens, routing, state management | Renders AI responses, insight cards, chat UI |
| **Express API Server** | REST endpoints, business logic, auth middleware | Constructs prompts, calls Claude API, returns results |
| **PostgreSQL Database** | Persistent storage for users, budgets, portfolios | Stores AI-generated profile summaries and insight history |
| **Claude API (Anthropic)** | LLM inference for all AI features | Onboarding, chat, budget insights, portfolio alerts |
| **Market Data Provider** | Stock quotes, historical data, news headlines | Feeds portfolio monitor and news translator |
| **Auth Service** | JWT-based session management | Protects all user data endpoints |
| **ML Recommendation Engine** | Predictive analysis (Phase 4) | Buy/hold/sell signals with confidence scores |

### 3.3 AI System Split

The AI layer is divided into two distinct subsystems:

- **Chat AI (LLM-based):** Education, conversation, Q&A, explanations, onboarding. Powered by Claude API with prompt engineering and context injection.
- **Recommendation Engine (Data-driven):** Financial logic engine with rule-based signals (Phase 2) evolving into ML model augmentation (Phase 4). Separate from the conversational AI.

