## 33. Safety, Age Compliance & Trust Guardrails

### 33.1 Financial Advice Guardrails

Finance Buddy is an **educational tool, not a licensed financial advisor**. The following guardrails must be enforced at both prompt and UI level:

- All Claude system prompts must explicitly state recommendations are educational, not financial advice.
- Every AI recommendation must include both potential upside and stated risk.
- The app must never execute a real trade in MVP — paper trading only.
- High-risk strategies (options, leverage, penny stocks) must not be suggested by the AI.
- Persistent UI disclaimer: *"Finance Buddy provides educational content only. Always consult a financial advisor before making real investment decisions."*

### 33.2 Age Verification

| ID | Priority | Requirement | Notes |
|----|----------|-------------|-------|
| SAFE-01 | MUST | Signup form must include checkbox: "I confirm I am 16 years of age or older" | |
| SAFE-02 | MUST | `ageConfirmed` must be `true` before account creation proceeds | |
| SAFE-03 | MUST | If `ageConfirmed` is `false`, return 403 with clear message | |
| SAFE-04 | PHASE 3 | Parental/guardian consent flow for users under 18 (jurisdiction-dependent) | |
| SAFE-05 | PHASE 3 | Restricted features for under 18: no real trading/broker integration, education + simulation only | |

