## 39. MVP Build Scope & Milestones

### 39.1 In Scope for Hackathon MVP

- User signup with age gate, login, JWT auth
- Buddy naming + onboarding quiz with Claude profile summary
- Dashboard with budget snapshot, savings goal, and at least one AI insight card
- Budget entry (income + expense), category display, AI budget insight
- Watchlist and paper portfolio (buy only) with live quotes from Polygon.io
- Claude-generated stock explanation per ticker
- AI chatbot with streaming, multi-turn context, and quick prompts
- At least 3 Learn lessons with Claude-generated content
- Personalized recommendation on dashboard based on risk profile
- ML auto-recommendations preview section with "Coming Soon" hub

### 39.2 Out of Scope for MVP

- Real money / brokerage integration
- OAuth social login
- Persistent chat history across sessions
- Recurring AI check-in digests (automated)
- Avatar / mascot animation
- Advanced portfolio analytics and charts
- Push notifications
- Double confirmation flow (Phase 2)
- Financial decision-making tools (Phase 2)
- ML predictive model (Phase 4)

### 39.3 Suggested Build Order

| Phase | Focus |
|-------|-------|
| **Build 1** | Auth, DB schema, User + UserProfile models, signup/login flow |
| **Build 2** | Onboarding quiz UI + Claude profile summary generation |
| **Build 3** | Budget tracker — entry CRUD, category display, AI insight endpoint |
| **Build 4** | Portfolio — Polygon.io integration, watchlist, paper buy, stock explain |
| **Build 5** | Chat — SSE streaming endpoint, chatbot UI, quick prompts |
| **Build 6** | Dashboard — assemble budget snapshot, portfolio value, insight cards |
| **Build 7** | Learn section — 3 lessons with AI-generated content |
| **Build 8** | Polish — error states, loading states, mobile responsiveness |

### 39.4 Definition of Done

The MVP is complete when a new user can: **sign up -> name their buddy -> complete onboarding -> see a personalized dashboard -> add a budget entry -> simulate buying a stock -> ask the chatbot a question** — all in a single uninterrupted flow.

