## 40. Full Development Roadmap

### Phase 1: MVP (8–12 weeks)
**Focus:** Learning + simulation — validate with real users.
- All items in Section 39.1
- Goal: demonstrate AI is central, not decorative

### Phase 2: Smart Guidance
**Focus:** Recommendation engine, behavioral coaching, trade safety.
- Rule-based recommendation engine with explainable signals
- Double process acceptance for trade confirmations
- Push notifications + alerts
- Structured learning modules with gamification
- Behavioral coaching (spending nudges, emotional investing warnings)
- Financial decision-making tools (bank selection, credit card comparison)
- User feedback loop (thumbs up/down, "was this helpful?")
- Persistent chat history

### Phase 3: Real Portfolio Integration
**Focus:** Brokerage connections, advanced finance tools, compliance.
- Broker API integrations (legal review required)
- Real-time alerts + full monitoring
- Advanced analytics + portfolio insights
- Savings plans and debt payoff planner
- Full notification strategy with anti-spam controls
- Plaid bank integration for auto-categorization
- GDPR/CCPA compliance implementation
- Offline/degraded experience
- PWA support

### Phase 4: Growth & Differentiation
**Focus:** ML engine, auto portfolio, full platform.
- ML predictive analysis engine (after months of training/research)
- Auto portfolio with opt-in/opt-out and granular controls
- Full risk & probability metrics on all recommendations
- Full gamification (levels, XP, badges, leaderboards)
- Social/community features (anonymized peer strategies)
- Personalized AI personality + animated avatar
- Native mobile apps (React Native or Flutter)
- Internationalization and multi-market support
- Advanced behavioral nudges + coaching
- Voice interaction

